 CHANTING]

00:00:12.220 --> 00:00:17.460 align:middle line:84%
>> So through the eyes love
attains the heart for the eyes

00:00:17.460 --> 00:00:20.700 align:middle line:90%
are the scouts of the heart.

00:00:20.700 --> 00:00:25.150 align:middle line:84%
And the eyes go reconnoitering
for what would please the heart

00:00:25.150 --> 00:00:25.950 align:middle line:90%
to possess.

00:00:25.950 --> 00:00:30.610 align:middle line:90%


00:00:30.610 --> 00:00:34.300 align:middle line:84%
And when they are in full
accord and firm, all three

00:00:34.300 --> 00:00:37.840 align:middle line:84%
in one resolve, at that
time perfect love is

00:00:37.840 --> 00:00:42.010 align:middle line:84%
born from what the eyes have
made welcome to the heart.

00:00:42.010 --> 00:00:46.420 align:middle line:90%


00:00:46.420 --> 00:00:57.000 align:middle line:10%
For as all true loves know,
love is perfect kindness

00:00:57.000 --> 00:01:00.825 align:middle line:10%
which is born there is no doubt
from the heart and the eyes.

00:01:00.825 --> 00:01:05.062 align:middle line:90%


00:01:05.062 --> 00:01:07.532 align:middle line:90%
